snippet.title: Actor GREG ELLIS And His SUPPORT For JOHNNY DEPP v Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Greg Ellis Joins me live to discuss his support for Johnny Depp regarding Amber Heard. Johnny Depp is innocent and after working with him on Pirates Of The Caribbean Greg Ellis is someone who can speak directly to the type of man Depp is.

This is outrageous and Johnny Deserves Justice!!!

Johnny Depp Tribute by Inspired with Johnny Depp - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JqNG_fS5CYg&t=1391s

Charity Link GOSH - https://www.justgiving.com/fundraising/stevie-j-raw1
